message.body: Hey Guys - the posters are ready! Let me know when you're back on campus / ready to poster?
Hey! - we're in the 8th entryway of Little right now (in front of Dillon) if you want to pick up your posters. Thanks for the quick response.
PS I love you and I was really sad I forgot to join the fantasy football league. My plan was to have all players with Hispanic last names
Do you want me to come now?
No problem at all! I can still add you as a secondary owner to a team if you would like. You can come if you want - depends on what your schedule is looking like
That would be cool, bro. Real cool. Also, I exaggerated a bit. I'm helping Ricky move in ATM. But we will come when done
